




0 - scaffold server folder using one of the template in https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/project-generation/
1 - use openai api for the core -> https://beta.openai.com/
2 - use static type checking for the core -> https://realpython.com/python-type-checking/
3 - build the app.py using https://typer.tiangolo.com/tutorial/package/
4 - complete uPC telebot using rust-lang to run python typer commands from rust using uPC telegram bot commands -> control process using pm2 or systemctl
5 - build the uniXerr desktop app inside board ui folder using vala -> https://wiki.gnome.org/Projects/Vala/Documentation
6 - pm2 start run.sh -> run tensorboard and uPC bot commands 



* next-section : api server, db folder, migrate command and /etc/hosts config